_sText:
de_saunatupa_talvi2 is a updated version of the map, including new passages to balance the map based on playtesting and feedback.

Counter-Terrorists: The sauna is being
heated up. An old radio plays in the
upstairs living room while the fireplace
crackles. A great day is ahead.

Terrorists: Plant the explosive device
in the sauna. The target needs to be
destroyed at all costs.
